README_HISTORY
This tar file contains all files needed for nemo_v3_4
forcing files COREII, normal year, interpolated on ORCA2 grid
downloaded from : http://data1.gfdl.noaa.gov/nomads/forms/mom4/COREv2/CNYF_v2.html
file version 15JUNE2009

files for AGRIF
        1_weight* : corresponding to weight for online interpolation of surface fluxes 
                    from the mother grid
                  ( 1_weights_bicub.nc : for bicubic interpolation for ORCA2 grid from core2 surface field's grid) 
                  ( 1_weights_bilin.nc : for bilinear    "    "      "    "     "    "    "    "   "   "   )
                  ( 1_weights_core2_agrif_bicubic.nc  : for bicubic interpolation for child grid from core2 forcing field's grid)
                  ( 1_weights_core2_agrif_bilinear.nc : for bilinear    "    "      "    "     "    "    "    "   "   "    "   " )
        1_dat*    :  3d LEvitus initialisation file
        1_bath_ymeter.nc : child grid bathymetry
        1_coordinates.nc : child grid coordinate
        1_K1rowdrg.nc    : Tidal energy for K1 tides (Sun) (mW/m2)
        1_M2rowdrg.nc    : Tidal energy for M2 tides (Moon) (mW/m2)
        1_data_1m_potential_temperature_nomask.nc : Levitus climatological potential temperature
        1_data_1m_salinity_nomask.nc              : Levitus climatological salinity
        1_geothermal_heating.nc : constant geothermal heat flux (mW/m2)
        AGRIF_FixedGrids.in : text file to specify the number and location of sub grids
                              this one correspond to an Agulhas zoom and has to be coherend 
                              with all 1_* files
